Package: fortuneblockd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - daemon
 Fortuneblock is an experimental new digital currency that enables instant, private
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Fortuneblock uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Fortuneblock Core
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides the daemon, fortuneblockd, and the CLI tool
 fortuneblock-cli to interact with the daemon.

Package: fortuneblock-qt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - Qt GUI
 Fortuneblock is an experimental new digital currency that enables instant, private
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Fortuneblock uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Fortuneblock Core
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides Fortuneblock-Qt, a GUI for Fortuneblock based on Qt.
